{"tid":1380123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《香城攻略》陣型戰術教學","createTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:47:02.000Z","uid":8948,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5945511aba61ad77cfcb32c85a00440d2749a7e4","tid":1380123,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:46:56.000Z","msg":"以下全部講緊香城online 或者 riot：civil unrest 既內容<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香城第一大原則：<br />\n保護他人之前，先保護好自己，自己裝備自己帶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>頭盔一定要有帽帶！背囊要揹前面！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oshc.hk/videos/1775100815919147\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foshc.hk%2Fvideos%2F1775100815919147&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67ZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=953fbdd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oshc.hk/videos/1775100815919147</a><br />\n<br />\n綜合左兩個月既遊玩經驗，以下綜合出兩款基本陣型<br />\n<br />\n1。防守陣型<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZGumMG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZGumMG.png&h=9557a6bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i2.kknews.cc/SIG=11sv2m3/o20002p580s24r5psr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2FSIG%3D11sv2m3%2Fo20002p580s24r5psr.jpg&h=91ef57be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2。攻擊型陣<br />\n＊游擊式＊be water＊<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/OXxtwsz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOXxtwsz.png&h=44058a56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HMsJyQmMbqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHMsJyQmMbqM&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67ZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=c480d29f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HMsJyQmMbqM</a><br />\n<br />\n祝各位早日打爆機<br />\n其餘基本裝備攻略一早已經出過，請趁呢幾日爬文籌備<br />\n<br />\n[721 廣傳] 兄弟爬山 對抗暴徒 物資採購攻略 - Decathlon<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324768\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324768</a><br />\n<br />\n【香城OL wiki】史上最全攻略！！持續更新！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/RBLoRU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/RBLoRU</a><br />\n<br />\n[721] 彩彈戰術，實測報告<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1325862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1325862</a>"},{"pid":"111b16a494849a1fa50bf79491435c8f1baf2ee8","tid":1380123,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:47:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"097cc10315f797f0b4c2913312142fabc4722f49","tid":1380123,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:47:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f22d8f8788d7642f2578bb7f7fe24e0942e62034","tid":1380123,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:48:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"256be406b3baf8b95477e5db3a97596fc8303db8","tid":1380123,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:48:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc49b8b5aea1eb93103096ae481a75351705b4a1","tid":1380123,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:48:50.000Z","msg":"南韓好慘<br />\n<br />\n由一班<strong>真男人</strong>變成成班&quot;拿型&quot;<br />\n<br />\n都唔知係咪政府搞鬼"},{"pid":"8aae9c2432a470bdeead877a22cf14cc0e6bd276","tid":1380123,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:50:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e6c5093fa87398aecfce7146e588679a319c6b9","tid":1380123,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:50:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f66ef6967198a69ec967f32270f84f1d1228201","tid":1380123,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply