 style=\"color: gold;\">香港政權真面目</span><br />\n西上環事件整合 求更多新聞同義士消息 推上去 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357053</a><br />\n我想問下葉虎單野係咪已有共識係炒咗車？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379219\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379219</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 光復香港 時代革命 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"c1479db9109be11b651071ad03c151e38064bf7f","tid":1380123,"uid":137461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:01:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5191645ea0ab51cff8d2b5d083ba73e5621e67d","tid":1380123,"uid":137461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:01:43.000Z","msg":"唔好比樓豬自己一個推晒"},{"pid":"fd1fab8b99a057490ba1f20726a42d735f9ef727","tid":1380123,"uid":137461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f48624b8d70f3b30a2e41b5119c6774929c42950","tid":1380123,"uid":137461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"其實現場好多人都唔識陣型戰術<br />\n點樣可以每次立即教識前線至少1-200人呢啲戰術"},{"pid":"f9aa80a5b3eebeef2015c125d946966000a857f4","tid":1380123,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f48624b8d70f3b30a2e41b5119c6774929c42950","tid":1380123,"uid":137461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:03:14.000Z","msg":"其實現場好多人都唔識陣型戰術<br />\n點樣可以每次立即教識前線至少1-200人呢啲戰術"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:13:32.000Z","msg":"每次落場都要教佢地<br />\n727 見到真係好多連背囊揹前都唔識既傻豬豬<br />\n每一位老手都有責任去教新手點保護自己"},{"pid":"f905e6f6fa4ce0cf39cfce586ddcf95ce3e2f771","tid":1380123,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:14:3